Numlock no ecrã do sddm:

$ sudo mkdir /etc/sddm.conf.d
$ sudo nano  /etc/sddm.conf.d/numlock.conf
[General]
Numlock=on

ZRAM:

$ sudo apt install zram-tools

$ ediroot /etc/default/zramswap
ALGO=zstd
PERCENT=100
PRIORITY=100

$ sudo zramswap start
